#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the top is a preview of the current theme icons. Most default "
"installations will have only a few icon theme available, amongst them the "
"&plasma; default Breeze theme. You can also download more from the Internet "
"from <ulink url=\"https://store.kde.org/\">https://store.kde.org/</ulink> or "
"install them from a local file."
msgstr ""
"Ku i Hejuru: , Urugero: Udushushondanga . Guhindura... in Imigaragarire ku i "
"Agashushondanga Insanganyamatsiko Guhitamo . Mburabuzi Rimwe Agashushondanga "
"Insanganyamatsiko Bihari , i &kde; Mburabuzi Insanganyamatsiko . Ibindi: in "
"i Porogaramu , na Iyimura Birenzeho Kuva: i . "

